The package libdwarfs provides CMake targets:

    find_package(dwarfs CONFIG REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE dwarfs::dwarfs_common dwarfs::dwarfs_reader dwarfs::dwarfs_writer)

Available targets:
  - dwarfs::dwarfs_common    - Core utilities, compression, serialization
  - dwarfs::dwarfs_reader    - DwarFS filesystem reading and FUSE driver
  - dwarfs::dwarfs_writer    - DwarFS filesystem creation
  - dwarfs::dwarfs_extractor - Filesystem extraction utilities